PHP-Docker
=====
This repository contains a collection of docker images usefull for developing in PHP. 

Base Image
-----
This repository was built with phusion/baseimage for a smaller, more proper base image for docker. In addition to the core ubuntu 14.04, this base image adds the following packages:
  * ca-certificates
  * inotify-tools
  * vim
  * pwgen
  * tmux
  * wget
  * telnet


####About
These Dockerfiles were inspired by:

    https://github.com/maxexcloo/Docker
    https://github.com/Painted-Fox/docker-mariadb
    https://github.com/phusion/baseimage-docker
